<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>بابُ أَصْرمَ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[١٦٦٤]</span> أَصْرمُ بنُ غِيَاثٍ النَّيْسَابُورِيُّ، أبو غِيَاثٍ <span class="c2">(١)</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>عن مُقاتلِ بنِ حيَّانَ الخُراسانيِّ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>مُنكَرُ الحديثِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c4">[١٦٦٥]</span> أَصْرَمُ بنُ حَوْشَبٍ <span class="c2">(٢)</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>مَتْروكُ الحديثِ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
